<p><br /></p>
<h4 id="about">About</h4>
<p>Build and share a bento box where your app’s features are the main course.</p>

<p>Crafting a brilliant marketing design should feel delightful, not dreadful. With Bento Craft, we’ve boxed up the complex and served up simplicity. Like arranging delicacies in a bento, organize your mockup elements with ease and style.</p>

<p>• Pre-made Bento Design - Think outside the box by designing inside ours!<br />
• Mini, Mega, and Max - Mockup making that’s as easy as picking sushi rolls.<br />
• Share in a Snap - Show off your delicious designs to the world.</p>

<p>Perfect for app developers and other creators, Bento|Craft is designed to be lightweight and effortless.<br />
<br />
== Features ==<br />
• Completely free to use<br />
• 3 Bento styles: Mini, Mega, and Max<br />
• Auto-add device frames to screenshots<br />
• Configurable text, images, and symbols<br />
• Easy export that can be shared anywhere<br />
• Supports participating Indie Devs through non-intrusive App Store ads (configurable)<br />
• And more</p>

